Package com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.provisioning.listener

Interface PushServiceListener

  • public interface PushServiceListener
    Listener to handle callbacks related to push notifications.
    See Also:
    ProvisioningServiceMessage, ProvisioningServiceError, Bundle

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      void onComplete()
      Callback method is invoked when the received push message processing is successfully finished.
      void onError​(ProvisioningServiceError error)
      Callback method invoked when error is occurred during the push message processing.
      void onServerMessage​(java.lang.String tokenizedCardId, ProvisioningServiceMessage message)
      Callback method is invoked when the server message is received and the required action is processed by the wallet.
      void onUnsupportedPushContent​(android.os.Bundle pushMessageBundle)
      Callback method is invoked when the push message is not supported by the SDK.

    • Method Detail

      • onError

        void onError​(ProvisioningServiceError error)
        Callback method invoked when error is occurred during the push message processing.
        Parameters:
        error - ProvisioningServiceError instance to indicating what error was raised

      • onUnsupportedPushContent

        void onUnsupportedPushContent​(android.os.Bundle pushMessageBundle)
        Callback method is invoked when the push message is not supported by the SDK.
        Parameters:
        pushMessageBundle - The message bundle from GCM.

      • onServerMessage

        void onServerMessage​(java.lang.String tokenizedCardId,
                     ProvisioningServiceMessage message)
        Callback method is invoked when the server message is received and the required action is processed by the wallet.
        Parameters:
        tokenizedCardId - the tokenized card ID that the message is for (optional). Null if the message is not linked to a specific card.
        message - message from CPS server.

      • onComplete

        void onComplete()
        Callback method is invoked when the received push message processing is successfully finished.
